Holy shit.

38
00:06:17.140 --> 00:06:18.140
Thai guy.

39
00:06:20.390 --> 00:06:21.390
Thai guy!

40
00:07:09.511 --> 00:07:11.845
Help me.

41
00:07:18.969 --> 00:07:21.552
